'''1949年德克萨斯飓风'''（{{lang-en|1949 Texas hurricane}}）是有纪录以来屈指可数的几个在太平洋形成，之后又进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]之一。风暴进入[[大西洋|大西洋盆地]]后开始增强，成为[[1949年大西洋飓风季|1949年大西洋飓风季]]的第十场热带风暴，之后的最高强度能达到现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]的二级飓风标准{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。10月4日早上，气旋从[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[弗里波特_(德克萨斯州)|弗里波特]]附近[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，然后急剧减弱，于数天后完全消散。

风暴造成中等程度破坏，[[加尔维斯敦_(德克萨斯州)|加尔维斯敦]]同德克萨斯州本土的交通一度中断。大面积水稻受损，损失数额估计有1000万美元（1949年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|10000000|1949}}}}美元），另有两人因这场飓风遇难。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|1949 Atlantic hurricane 11 track.png}}
现代分析结果显示，1949年9月27日清晨，[[萨尔瓦多|萨尔瓦多]]以南的太平洋发展出热带低气压。气旋向北移动，穿越[[中美洲|中美洲]]和[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]东部后于9月30日在[[卡门城|卡门城]]附近进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]。气象报告显示相应海域上空连续数天有[[低气压|低气压区]]存在。<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="MWR">{{cite journal | author = Richmond T. Zoch | title = North Atlantic Hurricanes and Tropical Disturbances of 1949 | date = 1949-12 | journal = Monthly Weather Review | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303190659/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/077/mwr-077-12-0339.pdf | deadurl = no | publisher = American Meteorological Society | volume = 77 | issue = 12 | accessdate = 2016-12-17 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/077/mwr-077-12-0339.pdf | format = PDF }}</ref>太平洋热带气旋进入大西洋的很少，大西洋热带气旋进入太平洋的也不多，1949年的这场风暴便是有正式纪录以来屈指可数的几个成为大西洋热带气旋的太平洋热带气旋之一<ref name="PacificQ&A">{{cite web | author = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | title = Subject: E15) What tropical storms and hurricanes have moved from the Atlantic to the Northeast Pacific or vice versa? | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-17 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E15.html | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303165250/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E15.html }}</ref>。除此以外，历史上只有三个热带气旋曾从东太平洋进入墨西哥湾<ref name="TX">{{cite web | author = David Roth | title = Texas Hurricane History | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2016-12-17 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/txhur.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161201044253/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/research/txhur.pdf | archivedate = 2016-12-01 | deadurl = no | format = PDF }}</ref>。

10月1日，气旋强化成飓风，并且增强速度还在转向西北期间略有提升，于一天后达到飓风标准。接下来风暴[[快速增强|快速增强]]，于10月3日逼近[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]海岸时达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时177公里的最高强度，在现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下属二级飓风强度，且已接近三级飓风标准。<ref name="HURDAT" />次日清晨，气旋从[[马塔哥达县|马塔哥达县]][[贝城_(德克萨斯州)|贝城]]（{{lang|en|Bay City}}）以东不远处上岸，估计此时[[气压|气压]]低至965[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.5[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），成为历史上屈指可数的几个在十月[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]或吹袭德克萨斯州的飓风之一<ref name="US hurricanes">{{cite web | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/UShurrs_detailed.html | title = Continental United States Hurricanes (Detailed Description) | author1 = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | author3 = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | date = 2015-02 | website = aoml.noaa.gov | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's Office of Oceanic & Atmospheric Research | location = Miami | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160828001543/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/UShurrs_detailed.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-08-28 | accessdate = 2016-12-16 }}</ref>。经过大幅减弱，风暴直接从[[休斯敦|休斯敦]]上空经过，之后要到[[1983年大西洋飓风季|1983年]]才有[[飓风艾丽西亚|飓风艾丽西亚]]从该市上空经过<ref name="books">{{cite book | author = Bryan Norcross | title = Hurricane Almanac: The Essential Guide to Storms Past, Present, and Future | year = 2007 | publisher = Macmillan | isbn = 0-312-37152-7 | url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=MlP71aeEPu0C&pg=PA59 | page = 59 | accessdate = 2016-12-17 | archive-date = 2018-10-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181005233918/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=MlP71aeEPu0C&pg=PA59 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

气旋在朝内陆行进期间快速减弱，登陆不到六小时就消退成热带风暴，然后转向东北继续经过美国中部，于10月5日弱化成热带低气压，再于次日转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，之后一直持续到10月7日才在[[威斯康辛州|威斯康辛州]][[希博伊根县_(威斯康辛州)|希博伊根县]]县城[[希博伊根_(威斯康辛州)|希博伊根]]（{{lang|en|Sheboygan}}）上空消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
飓风来袭前，德克萨斯州有来自十个城市的五万居民躲进避难所<ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Drives 50,000 From Homes | date = 1949-10-05 | newspaper = The Sydney Morning Herald | accessdate = 2016-12-17 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=EIsQAAAAIBAJ&sjid=F5MDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4977,737957&dq=1949+houston+hurricane&hl=en}}</ref>。其中休斯敦估计有2.8万人躲进避难所，约5000人待在市礼堂<ref>{{cite news | title = Gulf Hurricane Dies Out After Hitting Crops | date = 1949-10-05 | publisher = ''Pittsburgh Post-Gazette'' | accessdate = 2016-12-17 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=VygNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=QmoDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2016,1736405 | archive-date = 2017-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170305074308/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=VygNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=QmoDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2016,1736405 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。德克萨斯州和路易斯安那州沿海地区收到[[热带气旋警告|热带气旋警告]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Heading for Texas Coast | date = 1949-10-03 | newspaper = ''Miami News''}}</ref>。先锋航空将位于休斯敦的班机撤离，许多小型船只留在港口躲避<ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Smashes Into Texas Coast | date = 1949-10-04 | newspaper = Palm Beach Post}}</ref>。10月3日，[[科珀斯克里斯蒂_(德克萨斯州)|科珀斯克里斯蒂]]的学校停课，另有多家企业暂时关闭<ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Moves in on Texas Coast | date = 1949-10-03 | publisher = ''Spokane Daily Chronicle'' | accessdate = 2016-12-17 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=uAEaAAAAIBAJ&sjid=tfUDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6956,510078&dq=1949+texas+hurricane&hl=en}}</ref>。

飓风在弗里波特以西不远处产生时速217公里的强烈阵风，同时伴随着978毫巴（百帕，28.88英寸汞柱）气压和3.5米的风暴潮<ref name="TX" />。风暴降下暴雨，并以[[波尔克县_(德克萨斯州)|波尔克县]][[古德里奇_(德克萨斯州)|古德里奇]]（{{lang|en|Goodrich}}）雨量最高，达370毫米<ref name="MWR" />。降雨范围向东延伸至[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]，[[什里夫波特_(路易斯安那州)|什里夫波特]]降下173毫米雨量<ref name="Galveston">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Kills 2, Then Losses Force | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=eVwbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TE0EAAAAIBAJ&pg=3638,1637447&dq=1949+texas+hurricane+galveston+cut+off&hl=en | date = 1949-10-04 | publisher = ''The Pittsburgh Press'' | accessdate = 2016-12-17}}</ref>。城市地区普遍受到轻度破坏，休斯敦部分商铺的窗户被风刮破，街上四处散落着垃圾<ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Blasts Rich Texas Crops | date = 1949-10-04 | newspaper = Spokane Daily Chronicle | accessdate = 2016-12-17 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=uQEaAAAAIBAJ&sjid=tfUDAAAAIBAJ&pg=7144,824428&dq=1949+texas+hurricane&hl=en}}</ref>。海水漫过加尔维斯敦的海堤，该市同本土的交通一度中断。飓风催生的一场小型[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]袭击里斯维尔（{{lang|en|Riceville}}），导致两名儿童受伤。<ref name="Galveston" />另据报导，弗里波特受创最为严重，损失数额约为15万美元<ref>{{cite news | title = Two Are Killed In Texas Storm | date = 1949-10-05 | newspaper = Toledo Blade | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ZZ8TAAAAIBAJ&sjid=RQAEAAAAIBAJ&pg=5966,3647606&dq=1949+texas+hurricane+galveston+cut+off&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-12-17}}</ref>。

[[努埃塞斯县_(得克萨斯州)|努埃塞斯县]][[阿兰萨斯港_(德克萨斯州)|阿兰萨斯港]]（{{lang|en|Port Aransas}}）的一个码头基本被完全摧毁，损失数额约为一万美元。风暴还对当地的水稻、棉花和蔬菜作物构成重大破坏。<ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Fizzling Out After Blasting Texas | date = 1949-10-04 | newspaper = The Victoria Advocate | accessdate = 2016-12-17 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=TzUcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=DloEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6160,2351891&dq=1949+texas+hurricane+rice&hl=en}}</ref>气旋过去数天后，有报导估计受损的水稻约有50万[[蒲式耳|蒲式耳]]，损失数额达1000万美元<ref>{{cite news | title = Rice Crop Damaged | date = 1949-10-09 | publisher = ''The Pittsburgh Press'' | accessdate = 2016-12-17 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=fVwbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=TE0EAAAAIBAJ&pg=1491,3370840&dq=1949+texas+hurricane+rice&hl=en}}</ref>。不过，气象学家里士满·左奇（{{lang|en|Richmond T. Zoch}}）在1949年末的报告中指出，这场飓风造成的经济损失总额为670万美元<ref name="MWR" />。风暴过去后，来自六个州的成千上万辆汽车出现油漆剥落、起泡现象。起泡部分基本集中的汽车的引擎盖、挡泥板和车顶，泡中有少量水，什里夫波特还有一户民居出现油漆剥落现象。大部分受损车辆都是停在室外，遮挡好的汽车基本未受影响。虽然这类现象造成的损失可能有上万美元，但专家认为这还不属于飓风直接造成的损失。<ref>{{cite news | title = 'Plague' Hits Autos in Wake of Hurricane | date = 1949-10-07 | newspaper = Chicago Daily Tribune}}</ref>整场飓风共夺走两条人命，[[马塔戈达湾|马塔戈达湾]]（{{lang|en|Matagorda Bay}}）有一名青年女子溺毙，[[杰佛逊县_(德克萨斯州)|杰佛逊县]]的[[内奇斯港_(德克萨斯州)|内奇斯港]]（{{lang|en|Port Neches}}）有一位居民触电身亡<ref name="Galveston" />。

